ull to the doorway. Yes, rune skulls act like batteries, 'activating' the mechanisms in the castle as if it were Devil May Cry.Ya, so about that banshee. All of the hours my profile say that I have spent playing the game so far? ♥♥♥♥ing garbage! Back to square one! If you do pick it up, look up how to get the antidote, and get it ASAP!"
